Text: When word comes as to a more precise premiere date for the new Power Rangers season, I will post it in a comment under this torrent

Info update: The new series will be called "Power Rangers Samurai" and appears to be headed for a February 2011 premiere. Nothing is official, but the weekend of Feb. 5-6 looks like the target. Will update again when it gets locked down.
It's official -- PRS premieres on Nickelodeon in the USA on Monday, Feb, 7, 2011 at 8:00 p.m. Eastern time.
